KGUpEUDEIAnH6s5wQOpkOJI</a><br />\nNonpharmaceutical Measures for Pandemic Influenza in Nonhealthcare Settings&mdash;Personal Protective and Environmental Measures<br />\n<br />\nDisposable medical masks (also known as surgical masks) are loose-fitting devices that were designed to be worn by medical personnel to protect accidental contamination of patient wounds, and to protect the wearer against splashes or sprays of bodily fluids (36). There is limited evidence for their effectiveness in preventing influenza virus transmission either when worn by the infected person for source control or when worn by uninfected persons to reduce exposure. Our systematic review found no significant effect of face masks on transmission of laboratory-confirmed influenza.<br />\n<br />\nFauci講得啱，facemask只係比false security<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PRa6t_e7dgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPRa6t_e7dgI&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzqf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=c474057d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PRa6t_e7dgI</a><br />\nInfectious disease expert Dr. Anthony Fauci tells 60 Minutes: &quot;There's no reason to be walking around with a mask.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n個個戴咗mask，以為自己百毒不侵<br />\n唔想咁多人出街中病毒，應該行禁蒙面法，唔比帶mask，出親街等同簽生死狀寫定遺囑，街上自然會更少人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83405b42e241ac163deddb958a219722650bd227","tid":2236174,"uid":224771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3ba51f847a373b6368f08c33d11fbf1f7cfac10","tid":2236174,"uid":198583,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔：咁你即刻去慈雲山公廁有屎嘅廁所板舔十秒囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同呢班低學歷廢閪真係冇咩值得討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" c